.Sh NAME
.Nm buffy
.Nd Buffy the flouride dispenser game
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm Buffy
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
is a game of dental hygenic fun.  Use your randomly selected tool
on whatever creature happens your way to clean the fangs before
the flouride runs out.
.Pp
The game will choose a creature at random and a tool to clean the teeth.  The player
can choose simple tools or select from daggers for more powerful cleaning.
.Pp
.Sh GAMEPLAY
.Pp
You will clean the fangs one at time rotating through all four.  After completing cleaning
of four fangs, you may continue cleaning, skip a fang, quit, or save and quit.  You must
enter integer values for applying flouride.  
.Pp
Your score is printed out at the end.
